  "raw_html": "<button type='button' role='link' class='btn btn-link p-0 text-start' id='link_2' aria-label=\" Tata Mohan Rao versus S. Venkateswarlu and Others Etc. pdf\"  class='noToken' href='#' onclick=javascript:open_pdf('2','2025','2025_5_1375_1381','2025INSC678'); ><font size='4'> <strong>TATA MOHAN RAO<span class='fst-italic'> versus </span>S. VENKATESWARLU AND OTHERS ETC. </strong>- <span class='escrText'>[2025] 5 S.C.R. 1375</span><span class='ncDisplay'>2025 INSC 678</span><input type='hidden' id='cnr' value=ESCR010006062025></button></font><br><strong>Coram : BHUSHAN RAMKRISHNA GAVAI<sup style=\"color: #268e97;font-size: 22px;top: 0;\" class=\"tooltip-sup\" data-tooltip=\"Author\">*</sup>, AUGUSTINE GEORGE MASIH</strong><br> Issue for Consideration The Court was seized of a matter concerning the contemptuous conduct of a Tehsildar who forcibly evicted home dwellers and defied court orders. Court appreciated the factual scenario in light of principle of rule of law. Headnotes&dagger; Contempt of Court &ndash; of their houses via representation to revenue authorities &ndash; Not considered &ndash; Writ petitions filed against revenue authorities&rsquo; eviction attempt without considering Respondents&rsquo; representation &ndash; Direction to Appellant (the then Tehsildar) by High Court to<br><strong class='caseDetailsTD' ><span style='color:#212F3D' > Decision Date :</span><font color='green'> 09-05-2025</font><span style='color:#212F3D' > | Case No :</span><font color='green'> CIVIL APPEAL No. 6591/2025</font><span style='color:#212F3D' > | Disposal Nature :</span><font color='green'> Case Partly allowed</font>   <span style='color:#212F3D' > |  Bench :</span><font color='green'> 2 Judges</font></strong><div class='row my-1 mt-2 border bg-light'><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_splitview('2','2025','2025_5_1375_1381','2025INSC678','S')><i <i class='fas fa-columns me-2'></i>Split view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_splitview('2','2025','2025_5_1375_1381','2025INSC678','H'); ><i class='fas fa-file-alt me-2'></i>HTML view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_flip('2','2025','2025_5_1375_1381','2025INSC678');><i class='fas fa-book-open me-2' ></i>Flip view</a></div><div class='col-auto'><a href='#' class='btn btn-outline-secondary btn-sm my-1' onclick=open_pdf('2','2025','2025_5_1375_1381','2025INSC678','N'); ><i class='fas fa-file-pdf me-2'></i>PDF</a></div></div>",
